Structured black cap featuring the Eclipse logo.

Top it off in our structured black cap made of sturdy, durable brushed canvas. 100% cotton breathes for year-round comfort. Adjustable closure with a low profile crown. Images are permanently adhered with a sturdy patch. Look cool on bad hair days or when shading your eyes from the sun. One size fits most.

  • Adjusts from 20" to 24"
  • Crown measures 3 ¼"
  • Structured 100% brushed cotton canvas
  • Permanently adhered polyester patch

Stylish bag featuring the Eclipse logo.

From school, to carrying your laptop, to a hip alternative diaper bag, our versatile, spacious messenger bag is practically all you need to get you through every stage of your life and look hip doing it.

  • One front adjustable clasp closure.
  • Main compartment has inside slip pocket.
  • Front panel has zipper compartment.
  • 600 Denier Polyester
  • Size: 14 1/2" x 12" x 5"

100% cotton canvas with extra long handles. Measures 15" x 18" x 6".

Our 100% cotton canvas tote bags have plenty of room to carry everything you need when you are on the go. They include a bottom gusset and extra long handles for easy carrying.

  • 10 oz heavyweight natural canvas fabric
  • Full side and bottom gusset
  • 22" reinforced self-fabric handles
  • Machine washable
  • Measures 15" x 18" x 6"

Wire bound, 160-page journal. 5" x 8" with 24 lb. bond paper. Front cover is laminated for durabillity and back cover is thin black flexible plastic.

Scribble important stuff - lyrics, recipes, addresses, and more. Our Wire-O bound, 160 page journal has your choice of papers and measures 5" x 8", a handy on-the-go size to fit in your backpack. Get creative and let the muse flow.

  • Back cover made of thin black flexible textured plastic, measures 16/1000" thick
  • Front cover made of 12pt glossy paper, laminated for durability
  • Filled with your choice of 60lb bookweight (24 lb bond) paper -- blank, dot grid, lined college-ruled, or a task journal.

10" wall clock. Black plastic case. Includes 1 AA battery.

Decorate any room in your home or office with our 10 inch wall clock. Black plastic case. Requires 1 AA battery (included).

Sticker printed on 4mil vinyl using water and UV resistant inks, meaning no fading in the sun or bleeding in the rain. Featuring the Eclipse logo.

Our stickers are printed on 4mil vinyl using water and UV resistant inks – meaning no fading in the sun or bleeding in the rain.

  • Measures 3" x 5" oval
  • Printed on durable 4mil vinyl

1" diameter, metal shell button. Mylar/UV protecting cover and pinned metal back.

Add fun accents to jackets, backpacks, or mix 'n match our Mini Buttons. Our Mini Buttons are the perfect size for trading and collecting. Pin 'em on!

  • 1 inch diameter
  • Metal shell
  • Mylar/UV protecting cover
  • Pinned metal back

7" x 5" blank note cards.

Greeting cards are for more than holidays; they are a great way to express yourself and to keep in touch with friends and family. A personal note on a beautiful card will make a lasting impression and a touching keepsake.

  • Available in your choice of paper stock

    • High quality, chlorine and acid free matte paper consisting of 30% post consumer waste and 50% total recycled fiber
    • Twelve point, one-sided glossy paper
  • Ten cards per package/envelopes included
  • Measures 5" X 7"

100% cotton, open fly boxers from Robinson Apparel, featuring the Eclipse logo. Elastic waist band.

Enjoy the roomy comfort of our sexy boxers as underwear or sleepwear. They're 100% cotton, open fly for thinking outside the boxers. Boxers, because you don't want to be brief.

15oz ceramic mug featuring the Eclipse logo. Large handle for easy grasping. Dishwasher and microwave safe. Guaranteed.

Super-size your favorite beverage or just size-up to avoid spills with our hefty, 15 oz. ceramic Large Mug. Large easy-grip handle. When you need more, mug it up.

  • Measures 4.5" tall, 3.25" diameter
  • Dishwasher and microwave safe

Ceramic outer shell with stainless steel inner-sleeve. 7" tall and holds 15 oz. Fits its into most vehicle cub holders. Gasket-sealed lid with snap tight closure.

Love style? Then drink this up, because our eye -catching ceramic tumbler is a work of art. Plus it's also a workhorse -- thanks to a solid design with steel inner-sleeve that's ideal for hot or cold beverages. Holding a full 15 oz. and fitting into most vehicle's cup holders (includes snap-tight lid), it's also a great choice for travel.

  • Measures 7" tall
  • Holds 15 oz.
  • Ceramic outer shell, with stainless steel inner sleeve
  • Gasket-sealed lid, with snap tight closure
  • Hand wash only

22 oz. ceramic stein with gold trim.

Heft a cold one in this 22 oz. ceramic stein with gold trim. A great usable alternative to the trophy. Make any day Oktoberfest whether with this impressive stein on the shelf or in-hand. Cheers!

  • Measures 6.75" tall, 3.75" diameter base, 3" diameter rim
  • Dishwasher and microwave safe
